1.0.name: wordpress/tagebuch
1.0.description: Tagebuch is a responsive WordPress Theme built for modern browsers using HTML5 and CSS3. It supports high resolution displays, tablets, smartphones and other devices. Created by Alexander Geilhaupt of HTML Kombinat, Berlin.
